milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (309) involving teams New Zealand & Pakistan in ODIs
Pakistan's 6-run win against New Zealand is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 8-run win against West Indies
Lance Cairns has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (64) for NZ, going past Hadlee
